  - {fileID: 8300000, guid: 5b50f8daf50d9be49aa7ba458e4dcdba, type: 3}
  - {fileID: 8300000, guid: 797cf74cb972f7640a048711fad2e974, type: 3}
  - {fileID: 8300000, guid: 365d16e45ae2ca940bc1bd92db1ceba0, type: 3}
  - {fileID: 8300000, guid: e3f22b4078761f74aacc0a3430c59fa5, type: 3}
  - {fileID: 8300000, guid: f36f82f84e7bb6c4c8b87baa55fb6f62, type: 3}
  audioSourceBabble: {fileID: -1121092100325140080}
  stopAudioSource: 1
  minPitch: 0
  maxPitch: 1.2
  frequency: 2
  textComponet: {fileID: 1032148383272698172}
  linesIntro1:
  - Hm, so a goblin runs the counter now?
  - "You\u2019re smaller than I would expect... how old ARE you?"
  - (Meh.)
  - ...I see. I suppose even greatness can come in humble forms.
  linesIntro: []
  linesIntro2:
  - Ah, it's you again. Greetings, my little friend.
  - "Let\u2019s see how you\u2019ve improved, hm?"
  linesIntro3:
  - Greetings, my little friend.
  - As you know, I expect nothing less then perfect.
  - "Let\u2019s see if you keep up."
  linesPasstime:
  - It's interesting. So much can change in this place, yet the speakeasy itself
    stays the same.
  - I do wonder, my little friend, how long your presence here will last.
  - You're endearing enough, I suppose. There's hope for you yet.
  linesRight:
  - "This is\u2026 acceptable."
  - You may take pride in the creation of this potion.
  - We will see how you fare next time.
  linesWrong:
  - This is inadequate.
  - Worry not, my little friend... Perfection takes practice.
  linesEnd:
  - You have potential, little friend.
  - When I return, I hope to see that your skills have improved.
  textSpeed: 0.05
  potion: {fileID: 4202478232269582438}
  text: {fileID: 1248791015467373789}
  lines: []
  history: {fileID: 11400000, guid: ff918490d6c8d5843af075c7a34e9136, type: 2}
